data.description: You do not want to miss this 3 bedroom 2 bath bi level home on 5.71 wooded acres. The main level features a large open concept kitchen, dining room and living room with a large bay window, laundry/full bath, and 2 large bedrooms. The lower level features a large 15x30 family room with a wood burning fireplace, 1 bedroom with a master bath and a mud room that leads into the garage. This property includes a large back deck, central air, a pond and a large additional heated garage with a concrete floor. Don't miss this opportunity! Schedule a showing today.
